GBox2DX: C++ wrapper for Box2D and Cocos2d-x
-Based on the GBox2D repo by Andreas Loew

Usage:
-drop the GBoxDX repo into your cocos2d-x gles2.0 or later root folder
-add the GBox2DX library project and test projects into your cocos2dx solution
-update the project dependencies with "libGBox2D.lib"
-update GBox2D VS Project paths to cocos2d-x as needed

Android:
-also includes make file for shared or static library on android-ndk-r7b

